Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.94,0:01:44.20,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,一次次点燃时代的引信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.37,0:01:46.53,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,yeah boom 着火 no matter what you are
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.62,0:01:49.62,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,照天烧 burn the fire just set on the 火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.96,0:01:53.50,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,荒唐无稽的上进心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.58,0:01:55.38,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,空中漂浮 现在Time to time
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.54,0:01:57.71,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,一心不乱加坚忍不拔 alright
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.96,0:01:59.63,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.80,0:02:01.63,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,不是孤身一人 let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.67,0:02:04.93,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,不要停下 来创造未来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.30,0:02:12.31,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,如夜里的花一般 无人欣赏也绽放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.02,0:02:18.82,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,从过去继承的flame 在胸口沉睡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.98,0:02:19.78,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,感受它
